  <h1 class="tutorial-header">How to Use Mammoth Task</h1>
  <div class='current-screenshot-instruction'>
    <p>To master Mammoth Task.. First simply choose to Create a custom project or Manage your progress.<br> We suggest, if you are new to Mammoth task, to Create a new Project first.
    </p>

    <img src="assets/createFirst.png" class="currentSS" alt="Landing Page" />
   </div>


